Technical Specifications:
- AES-128/256 encryption in CBC mode
- Streaming I/O with 1MB chunks
- PKCS7 padding implementation
- PBKDF2 key derivation with SHA-256
- Random salt and IV generation per file

Performance Features:
- Memory-optimized processing (~60% reduction in peak usage)
- Support for files up to 50MB+ on standard laptops
- Cross-platform compatibility (Windows, macOS, Linux)
- CLI interface with comprehensive error handling

Security Features:
- Industry-standard AES encryption
- Secure password-based key derivation
- Unique salt and IV per encryption operation
- Protection against common cryptographic attacks

